      <div class="bg-white border border-yellow-400 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 p-8">
        <div class="text-6xl text-yellow-400 opacity-20">“</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The PELRC internship completely transformed my approach to web development.
