                                web application.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="secondary-button">Reserve Spot
                                (₹1,499)</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="workshop-card" data-animate="fade-up"
                        data-animate-delay="0.4s">
                        <div class="workshop-date">
                            <span class="date-day">22</span>
                            <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="workshop-info">
                            <h3>Python for Beginners</h3>
                            <p class="workshop-meta"><i
                                    class="fas fa-clock"></i> 10AM - 4PM | <i
                                    class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                                Online</p>
                            <p>Master Python basics and build your first
                                automation scripts.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="secondary-button">Reserve Spot
                                (₹999)</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="workshop-card" data-animate="fade-up"
                        data-animate-delay="0.5s">
                        <div class="workshop-date">
                            <span class="date-day">29</span>
                            <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="workshop-info">
                            <h3>CAD & Simulation Basics</h3>
                            <p class="workshop-meta"><i
                                    class="fas fa-clock"></i> 10AM - 4PM | <i
                                    class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                                Bangalore</p>
                            <p>Hands-on CAD practice using SolidWorks or AutoCAD
                                for mechanical design.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="secondary-button">Reserve Spot
                                (₹1,799)</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact/CTA Section -->
        <section id="contact" class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cta-content" data-animate="fade-up">
                    <h2>Ready to Launch Your Career?</h2>
                    <p>Reach out to PELRC — we're here to help you get
                        started.</p>

                    <form id="contactForm" class="application-form"
                        method="post" action="/auth/api/send/inquiry">
                        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Full Name"
                            required />
                        <input type="email" name="email"
                            placeholder="Email Address" required />
                        <input type="text" name="message"
                            placeholder="Your Message" required />
                        <button type="submit" class="primary-button">Send
                            Message</button>
                    </form>

                    <!-- Flash message -->
                    <div id="flashMessage"
                        class="bg-yellow-100 border border-yellow-400 text-yellow-800 text-center font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md mt-4 hidden shadow-md">
                        Message sent successfully!
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

